OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781053389
OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FA senior officer said police in the
OL,7,Fregion are currently dealing with
OL,8,F"sporadic pockets of disorder" in a
OL,9,Fnumber of locations.
OL,11,FMasked males set commercial bins
OL,12,Falight and pushed them into the Glider
OL,13,Fbus on the Newtownards Road in the
OL,14,Feast of the city on Tuesday evening.
OL,16,FIt came as a large crowd gathered in
OL,17,Fthe area.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@^O]
