OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FTranslink, which operates public
OL,7,Ftransport services in the region,
OL,8,Fcondemned the incident and said all
OL,9,Fbus and train services were being
OL,10,Fsuspended for the evening.
OL,12,FDemonstrations are taking place in
OL,13,Fareas across Northern Ireland
OL,14,Ffollowing Monday night's incident.
OL,16,FThere are multiple reports of roads
OL,17,Fbeing blocked and vehicles being set
OL,18,Falight in Belfast and some other areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
