OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FIn Lendrick Street in Belfast, several
OL,7,Fcars were set alight and Northern
OL,8,FIreland Fire and Rescue Service
OL,9,Fofficers had to remove some residents
OL,10,Ffrom houses after they caught fire.
OL,12,FA number of houses and vehicles are
OL,13,Fcurrently on fire near the Ligoniel
OL,14,FRoad area of Belfast.
OL,16,FUnionist MLA Doug Beattie said a
OL,17,Fpolice car had been set on fire in
OL,18,FPortadown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
