OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781053389
OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FShe said: "They are intent on wreaking
OL,7,Fdestruction on the very communities
OL,8,Fthey claim they are trying to protect.
OL,10,F"They are weaponising the genuine
OL,11,Fhurt, concern and anger that people
OL,12,Fare feeling for their own misguided
OL,13,Fpurposes.
OL,15,F"There is no place for masked thugs to
OL,16,Ftake to the streets and threaten,
OL,17,Fintimidate, disrupt and cause wanton
OL,18,Fdamage ` it is simply disingenuous to
OL,19,Fclaim this is being carried out for
OL,20,Fthe good of Northern Ireland."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUwD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
