OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FShe added: "I would appeal once again
OL,7,Fto communities not to allow themselves
OL,8,Fto be used and abused in this manner.
OL,10,F"Disorder on the streets, such as we
OL,11,Fare seeing tonight, is diverting
OL,12,Fvaluable police resources away from
OL,13,Fthose who genuinely need them.
OL,15,F"These are not the actions of people
OL,16,Fwho genuinely care about their
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
