OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781053389
OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,F"While I recognise and understand the
OL,7,Fconcerns following on from the attack
OL,8,Fin north Belfast, hate cannot be
OL,9,Fallowed to win."
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister
OL,12,FMichelle O'Neill has described scenes
OL,13,Fof violence in Belfast as "outright
OL,14,Fthuggery".
OL,16,FIn a social media post, Ms O'Neill
OL,17,Fsaid: "Groups of masked men burning
OL,18,Ffamilies out of their homes is nothing
OL,19,Fless than disgusting cowardice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@PO]uD@[OUvD@IO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
