CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781053389
OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,F"This has nothing to do with
OL,7,Fcommunity. This is outright thuggery.
OL,9,F"The attack in North Belfast was
OL,10,Fheinous and wrong.
OL,12,F"But there are dangerous attempts to
OL,13,Fexploit that to target and attack
OL,14,Finnocent people who are simply trying
OL,15,Fto live, work and raise their families
OL,16,Fhere.
OL,18,F"Racism, intimidation and violence are
OL,19,Fwrong wherever they occur.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
