OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781053389
OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,F"There can be no excuse and no
OL,7,Fjustification for these attacks
OL,8,Ftonight."
OL,10,FIn a social media post, Northern
OL,11,FIreland's deputy First Minister Emma
OL,12,FLittle-Pengelly said violence does not
OL,13,F"advance any cause, it damages it".
OL,15,FShe added: "Destroying things within
OL,16,Fyour own community benefits no one.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]uD@AOUuD@bO]wD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
