OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,F"Taking frustration at the evil
OL,7,Factions of a person out on those who
OL,8,Fhad no part in it is utterly wrong.
OL,9,FSafety is at the heart of so much of
OL,10,Fthe concern.
OL,12,F"Engaging in violence risks your own
OL,13,Fsafety, that of others and
OL,14,Ffundamentally does any cause or
OL,15,Fcampaign to be heard terrible
OL,16,Fdisservice and damage."
