OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FThere has been widespread condemnation
OL,7,Fof Monday night's knife assault.
OL,9,FPolice commanders and political
OL,10,Fleaders had appealed for calm amid
OL,11,Fconcern the planned anti-immigration
OL,12,Fprotests would turn violent.
OL,14,FDetectives have said there is no
OL,15,Findication Monday's knife attack was
OL,16,Fterror-related.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
