OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fhas launched a "critical incident" in
OL,8,Fresponse to the incident which was
OL,9,Fcaptured on video and appears to show
OL,10,Fa man stabbing at the victim's head
OL,11,Fand neck while he was lying on the
OL,12,Fground.
OL,14,FThe clip shows people, including one
OL,15,Fwith a hurling stick, intervening to
OL,16,Fstop the man attacking the victim in
OL,17,Fthe Kinnaird Avenue residential area
OL,18,Fclose to the busy Antrim Road in north
OL,19,FBelfast.
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
