OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FA kitchen knife was recovered from the
OL,7,Fscene.
OL,9,FEarlier on Tuesday, police revealed
OL,10,Fdetails on the arrested man's
OL,11,Fimmigration status and how he
OL,12,Ftravelled to the UK.
OL,14,FHe entered Northern Ireland across the
OL,15,FIrish border in February 2023 having
OL,16,Fflown to Dublin from Paris.
OL,18,FThe suspect claimed asylum upon
OL,19,Farrival and in September 2023 was
OL,20,Fgranted leave to remain in the UK
OL,21,Funtil 2028.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
