OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781053389
OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher
OL,7,Fbriefed reporters on the status of the
OL,8,Finvestigation as he appeared alongside
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister
OL,10,FMichelle O'Neill, Ms Little-Pengelly
OL,11,Fand Ms Long at a press conference at
OL,12,FStormont on Tuesday afternoon.
OL,14,FCommenting on the prospect of
OL,15,Fdisorder, the police chief warned
OL,16,Fpeople against being influenced "from
OL,17,Fafar through social media".
OL,26,@xD@aOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
