OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781053389
OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,F"I have absolutely no tolerance for
OL,7,Fabhorrent scenes of violence like this
OL,8,Fon our streets.
OL,10,F"My thoughts are first and foremost
OL,11,Fwith the victim, and I thank the first
OL,12,Fresponders, including members of the
OL,13,Fpublic who intervened."
OL,15,FLater, the leaders of the five largest
OL,16,Fparties at Stormont issued a joint
OL,17,Fstatement in response to the attack.
