OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FSinn Fein vice president Ms O'Neill,
OL,7,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson, Alliance
OL,8,FParty leader Ms Long, UUP leader Jon
OL,9,FBurrows and SDLP leader Claire Hanna
OL,10,Fsaid they were "united in our
OL,11,Fcondemnation of the horrific incident
OL,12,Fin North Belfast last night".
OL,14,FThe political leaders urged anyone
OL,15,Fwith information that could help the
OL,16,Fpolice investigation to assist
OL,17,Fdetectives.
OL,19,FThey also issued an appeal for calm.
