OL,3,CLeaders call for calm as violence
OL,4,Cflares following Belfast knife attack
OL,6,FThe scene outside an apartment complex
OL,7,Foff Kinnaird Avenue remained cordoned
OL,8,Foff on Tuesday, with markers visible
OL,9,Fon the ground where the attack had
OL,10,Ftaken place.
